---
import Section from "../../components/common/Section.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { GLOBAL } from "../../lib/variables";
---

<Layout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>{GLOBAL.aboutTitle} • {GLOBAL.username}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={GLOBAL.aboutShortDescription} />
    <meta property="og:title" content={`${GLOBAL.aboutTitle} • ${GLOBAL.username}`} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={GLOBAL.aboutShortDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={`${GLOBAL.rootUrl}/${GLOBAL.aboutImage}`} />
    <meta property="og:image:alt" content="Profile picture of Jesús Sanz" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={`${GLOBAL.rootUrl}/about`} />
    <meta http-equiv="content-language" content="en" />
    <meta name="language" content="English" />
    <link rel="canonical" href={`${GLOBAL.rootUrl}/about`} />
  </Fragment>

  <Section class="py-4 my-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-8 pb-16">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-loose">{GLOBAL.aboutName}</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full my-6">
      <img 
        src={`${GLOBAL.rootUrl}/${GLOBAL.aboutImage}`}
        alt="Full-width profile" 
        class="w-full max-h-[400px] rounded-xl shadow-lg object-cover object-center"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-justify text-left">
      <p>
        Hi! I’m a <strong>frontend developer</strong> with over 8 years of experience, focused on building <strong>high-performance</strong>, <strong>accessible</strong>, and <strong>SEO-optimized</strong> web applications using <strong>Angular</strong>, <strong>React</strong>, and modern development tools.
      </p>
      <p>
        I currently work as a Senior Developer at <strong>Hiberus Technology</strong>, where I lead performance optimization, UI/UX best practices, and scalable frontend architecture. I’m also a certified Scrum Master and help connect frontend and backend teams effectively.
      </p>
      <p>
        In past roles, I’ve built full-stack enterprise apps with technologies like .NET, SQL, Vue, and React, collaborating across multicultural teams.
      </p>
      <p>
        My background in <strong>social education and coordination</strong> has given me valuable mentoring and facilitation skills, which I bring into every team environment.
      </p>
      <p>Here’s a snapshot of my skill set:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Angular, React, HTML5, CSS, JavaScript</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, SQL</li>
        <li><strong>Tools:</strong> Git, CI/CD, Angular Schematics, Jest, Scrum</li>
        <li><strong>Soft skills:</strong> Teamwork, leadership, adaptability</li>
        <li><strong>Languages:</strong> Spanish (native), English (C1)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-justify text-left mt-6">
      <p>
        When I’m not coding, you’ll probably find me outdoors — hiking, surfing, or exploring nature. It keeps me grounded, fuels my creativity, and reminds me to always think sustainably.
      </p>
      <p>
        Always open to new ideas, projects, or just chatting about tech and design. You’ll find my contact links in the footer!
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>